# Animations (GSAP)

Allowed: opacity, translate, scale, clip-path, mask reveal, scroll pinning, text split, card stagger, SVG line draw, counters.

Avoid: excessive parallax, bouncing, spinning icons, flashy transitions.

Feel: Apple, Linear, Stripe — not marketing template.

Always check `prefers-reduced-motion: reduce` and skip animations.
Lazy-load GSAP — dynamic import only in client components.
ScrollTrigger only on landing app, not dashboard.
